  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this multicentre prospective trial is to determine the incidence and risk
      factors for surgical wound infections. Also the investigators will evaluate consequences of
      wound infections to the patients, and extra costs caused by wound infections.
    </textblock>
